Judul: HAUL OF MYSTERIOUS COSMIC BURST EXCITES ASTRONOMERS
Abstrak:
Astronomers are edging closer to finding out what causes brief, powerful flashes
in the sky known as fast radio bursts (FRBs), after a Canadian telescope discovered
eight more of the most intriguing type of these blasts — those that repeat their signals.
FRBs are intensely energetic events
Fakultas: Fakultas Matematika dan Ilmu Pengetahuan Alam
